                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17171204-11-off58 t17171204-11-cd59"></join> last. The Prosecutor deposed that being in Bed and asleep, his Wife heard the Bolt of the Door fall on the Ground, and waked him, and immediately called out to know who was there, and was answer'd a Friend, her Brother: His Wife confirm'd this, adding, she immediately jump'd out of Bed, running into the next Room in her Shift, catching hold of one of the two Men that were in the Room by the Coat, but he got from her, and they slipping by her ran away and got off, and afterwards seeing the Petticoat hang up at a Broker's challeng'd it, who sent for one 
